JBHI bhi ye scenetio ho ki you have to choose one in 2 options for miximizing value and minimizing value 
go with DP

 DP ki problems me we have 
 1. base condition 
            - hmesha jo bhi problem di ho iski sbko smallest value jobhi posssible ho paye rkh ke dekho vhi base        condition h
2.  main function 
            - Problem solve karo by combining results of smaller subproblems.
            - Yahan aap decision logic apply karte ho to maximize ya minimize result.
3.  return statement
            - Function ya DP table se computed value return karo.
            - Ye subproblem ka result ya final answer ho sakta hai.


***PROBLEM ko TREE ke form me build kro 